{"title":"linux学习笔记","uid":"c42ea271ec848445301016f3b979e666","slug":"linux","date":"2022-03-01T12:24:19.280Z","updated":"2022-04-17T01:12:31.764Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/linux.json","keywords":"笔记","cover":[],"content":"<h1 id=\"一-linux相关命令\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#一-linux相关命令\"></a> 一 linux相关命令</h1>\n<h2 id=\"1-whatis\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#1-whatis\"></a> 1. whatis</h2>\n<h3 id=\"显示在线手册说明\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#显示在线手册说明\"></a> 显示在线手册说明</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><img src=\"../images/linux/image-20220303180648572.png\" alt=\"image-20220303180648572\"></li>\n<li>print name of current/working directory  打印当前/工作目录的名称<br>\nlist directory contents   列出目录的内容</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"2-ls\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#2-ls\"></a> 2. ls</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><img src=\"../images/linux/image-20220303181453565.png\" alt=\"image-20220303181453565\"></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"列出目录的内容\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#列出目录的内容\"></a> 列出目录的内容</h3>\n<h2 id=\"3-cd\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#3-cd\"></a> 3. cd</h2>\n<h3 id=\"改变工作目录\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#改变工作目录\"></a> 改变工作目录</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><img src=\"../images/linux/image-20220303181927398.png\" alt=\"image-20220303181927398\"></li>\n<li>cd test 进入test目录</li>\n<li>cd …  返回上级目录</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"4-cp\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#4-cp\"></a> 4. cp</h2>\n<h3 id=\"copy-files-复制文件\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#copy-files-复制文件\"></a> copy files  复制文件</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><img src=\"../images/linux/image-20220303182615469.png\" alt=\"image-20220303182615469\"></li>\n<li>cp hello.c hello2.txt  （cp 复制文件 重命名该文件）</li>\n<li>cp -r csource csource001 (cp 复制文件夹 重命名该文件夹)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"5-less\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#5-less\"></a> 5. less</h2>\n<h3 id=\"查看文件\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#查看文件\"></a> 查看文件</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><img src=\"../images/linux/image-20220303183443796.png\" alt=\"image-20220303183443796\"></li>\n<li><img src=\"../images/linux/image-20220303183411120.png\" alt=\"image-20220303183411120\"></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"6-head-tail\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#6-head-tail\"></a> 6. head tail</h2>\n<h3 id=\"查看文件的开头或结尾\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#查看文件的开头或结尾\"></a> 查看文件\t的开头或结尾</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><img src=\"../images/linux/image-20220303183843025.png\" alt=\"image-20220303183843025\"></li>\n<li>head -n 1 hello.c\n<ul>\n<li>查看hello.c文件里的第一行内容</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>tail -n 1 hello.c\n<ul>\n<li>查看hello.c文件里的倒数第一行内容</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"7-find\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#7-find\"></a> 7. find</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>查找过滤文件</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"在目录层次结构中搜索文件\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#在目录层次结构中搜索文件\"></a> 在目录层次结构中搜索文件</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><img src=\"../images/linux/image-20220303184446937.png\" alt=\"image-20220303184446937\"></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"8-cat\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#8-cat\"></a> 8. cat</h2>\n<h3 id=\"合并多个文件夹\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#合并多个文件夹\"></a> 合并多个文件夹</h3>\n<h3 id=\"查看文件夹里的内容\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#查看文件夹里的内容\"></a> 查看文件夹里的内容</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><img src=\"../images/linux/image-20220303184851505.png\" alt=\"image-20220303184851505\"></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"9-cal\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#9-cal\"></a> 9. cal</h2>\n<h3 id=\"显示当前日历\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#显示当前日历\"></a> 显示当前日历</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><img src=\"../images/linux/image-20220303185617159.png\" alt=\"image-20220303185617159\"></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"10-which\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#10-which\"></a> 10. which</h2>\n<h3 id=\"定位文件的存放路径\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#定位文件的存放路径\"></a> 定位文件的存放路径</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><img src=\"../images/linux/image-20220303190014352.png\" alt=\"image-20220303190014352\"></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"11-whereis\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#11-whereis\"></a> 11. whereis</h2>\n<h3 id=\"定位程序帮助手册的存放路径\"><a class=\"markdownI